    SubscriptBox["t", "2"]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "d2f368e6-e4ec-421c-be0c-d611c36b04b0"],
 ") are encoded by integers, then converted into alphabetic format only in \
the printed analytical expressions. The index conversion map is provided by"
}], "Text",
